message: The COMPARABILITY field for indicator 16-6-2, translated into all languages

data.en: This indicator corresponds to the global SDG target “16.6.1: Primary government expenditures as a proportion of original approved budget, by sector (or by budget codes or similar)”.
data.vi: Chỉ tiêu này tương ứng với chỉ tiêu SDG toàn cầu “16.6.1: Primary government expenditures as a proportion of original approved budget, by sector (or by budget codes or similar)”.
